      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless inside and out, with that 'new car' feel still going strong. I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of it, so you can just hop in and enjoy the smooth, flawless drive. It\u2019s truly a rare find in this kind of pristine shape. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
