      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true showroom-quality vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that is absolutely flawless\u2014free of swirls, stone chips, or any imperfections\u2014and has been preserved under a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero signs of wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete and meticulous service history documented by the dealership. It has been strictly garage-kept, never driven in inclement weather, and is entirely free of modifications. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this non-smoker, low-mileage example is the ultimate find. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a pristine title.",
